  <h3 id="How-to-unpublish-a-product-O3J0X">How to unpublish a product</h3>
  <p>To unpublish a product, </p>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to your <a href="https://gumroad.com/products/">Product's Dashboard</a>, </li>
    <li>Select the product you'd like to unpublish </li>
  </ol>
  <p>Click the Unpublish button on the top of the page.</p>
  <figure><%= image_tag "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/mgXG62eOz04eP2MJguqg7QAHz7KciiZQM8kEIUg3qMxo1j79HCWbnee-n54ndZaCGCPaGCmmY_IpS4r9sXYwWkSBEs-bZf0Hi0mybQXfdG7iZ1PVOFdN8y_E82k0RV6bTDdtNdjyzDO1Pwhw5A", width: 624, height: 313 %></figure>
  <p>When you unpublish your product:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Customers are no longer able to purchase it.</li>
    <li>The product is removed from Gumroad Discover.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Unpublishing does not delete your product or any data associated with it. Your product will remain the same as how you designed it; this simply removes the product from the customer-facing view.</p>
  <p>Customers who have bought the product will still be able to access their files. </p>
  <h3 id="How-to-delete-a-product-xArOg">How to delete a product</h3>
  <p>To delete one of your products:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to your <a href="https://gumroad.com/products">Product Dashboard</a>.</li>
    <li>Click the three-dot menu (⋯) on the product you want to delete.</li>
    <li>Select <b>Delete permanently</b>.</li>
    <li>Confirm the deletion when prompted.</li>
  </ol>
  <p><b>Note:</b> Deleting a product is permanent and cannot be undone. If you're unsure, consider <a href="#How-to-unpublish-a-product-O3J0X">unpublishing</a> the product instead.</p>
  <h3 id="After-deleting-the-product-jT6vp">After deleting the product</h3>
  <p>Your customers will still have access to the files they purchased, but you will not be able to see them in your Audience tab. They will also not show up in the <a href="74-the-analytics-dashboard">exportable CSV of your sales</a>. </p>
  <h3 id="Deleting-a-membership-product-mwaed">Deleting a membership product</h3>
  <p>Deleting a membership product cancels everyone's subscription. </p>
